# Allowlist approach: ignore everything, then re-include only deployable files.
# Keeps raw photos (877MB), transcripts, notes, and PDFs out of the public repo.
*

!.gitignore
!.nojekyll
!index.html
!landing-cpff.html
!landing-kenrusk.html

!assets/
!assets/**

!images/
images/*
!images/web/
!images/web/**
